<p>Hi! I'm <strong>{{ site.author }}</strong>, and welcome to {{ site.title }}. This blog is my space for sharing knowledge about open source hardware development, with a focus on RISC-V processors, FPGA design, Zephyr RTOS, and the powerful open source tools that drive modern embedded systems.</p>

