<h2>Why Open Source Hardware?</h2>
<p>Open source hardware enables:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> Understand exactly how your hardware works</li>
  <li><strong>Customization:</strong> Modify designs to fit your specific needs</li>
  <li><strong>Education:</strong> Learn from real-world, production-quality designs</li>
  <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> Build on the work of others to create something new</li>
  <li><strong>Cost-effectiveness:</strong> Leverage free tools and community support</li>
</ul>

